channel.title: "[KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server!"?
channel.description:
Ok,while i was hosting my server editing it etc etc, when i rebooted my comp.
So after i rebooted i treid to load up mopar 2...
wouldnt load, just a gray screen nothing else, stood like that for 5 minutes.
so i treid mopar 3.
after 3 minutes it sucessfully loaded and i clicked to run my server...
whne i ran my server the client lagged HORRIBLY,so i closed it out.
treid mopar 2 again, some thing.
then in my runeserver it says a whole bunch of times over and over again:
[KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server! [KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server! [KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server! [KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server! [KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server! [KERNEL]: machine is too slow to run this server!
Yes, i do speak english i just want to know, what dose this exactly mean?
Thanks in advance for any help provided.
